Check before run
================

* Check where is your mesh file
* Check what verion of openmoi (or other MPI library) are you using

Example run
===========
mpirun -np 2 ./mesh_smoothing -my_file chees.cub  \
  -ksp_type fgmres -pc_type asm -sub_pc_type lu -ksp_atol 1e-10 -ksp_rtol 1e-12 \
  -snes_monitor -snes_type ls -snes_linesearch_type l2 -snes_max_it 100 -snes_atol 1e-8 -snes_rtol 1e-8 -snes_converged_reason \
  -my_penalty 1e12 -my_gamma 0 -my_alpha2 1 -ksp_monitor
